_sText:
Put txt, bsp and ztmp files in your 
\SIERRA\half-life\counter-strike\SteamApps\"username"\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps folder.
This map was made the 14th of May 2005 by ogsh.


Map description:

The upper level of the map is a cind of jumping area.
 If you jump the right way, you get to lots of weapons 
 (including the only para, M4A1s and flashbangs on the map).
